data.description: Experience comfort and style at 4421 So R Cir, Fort Smith, AR. This 4-bed, 3.5-bath home on a cul-de-sac offers 2608 sq ft of living space, including a heated/cooled sunroom. Enjoy the inground pool, hot tub, and modern amenities like 2 HVAC units. Recent upgrades: new hot water heater, roof, gutters, and deck. House is being sold "as is", however, a full-price offer includes a $7,700 allowance for new pool liner and replace tub in bathroom. Centrally located, this property combines tranquility with convenience. Make 4421 So R Cir your new home.
